      • viewFinancingOptions

        public static void viewFinancingOptions(java.util.ArrayList<Car> carList)
        This method allows the user to view financing options for a car in an ArrayList of Car objects. It performs basic calculations to find monthly payment amounts for payments spanning 36 months at an 11% interested rate as well as the monthly payments for payments spanning 48 months at a 9% interest rate.
        Parameters:
        carList - An ArrayList of Car objects.
        Since:
        2020-24-06
